    title: '1099 Tax Product Lead',
    content:
      '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Stripe builds the most powerful and flexible tools for running an internet business. We handle billions of dollars each year and enable millions of users around the world to scale faster and more efficiently by building their businesses on Stripe. More than half of US internet users have purchased something from a Stripe user in the past year.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;For example, Connect is Stripe’s leading product for marketplaces, on-demand services, ecommerce site builders, invoicing platforms, professional SaaS products, fundraising platforms, rental management platforms, and more.&amp;nbsp; By utilizing the power of Connect, users in each of these categories can link multiple parties for the exchange of goods and services. While products like Connect aim to simplify the ability to move money around the world for our users, behind the scenes, Stripes across the company work together to weave in and satisfy applicable laws and regulations, tax being one!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a world class 1099 tax specialist who loves solving complex problems with cross functional teams to come up with and implement elegant product solutions that help with satisfying the 1099-K, 1099-NEC, and 1099-MISC tax obligations of Stripe users.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Be the lead tax subject matter expert supporting the development of Stripe’s 1099 product, providing advice regarding tax requirements and system designs while having a strong moral compass and integrity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work closely with product and engineers to strategize, build, test, and market tax technology solutions for 1099 reporting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Support internal user facing teams, such as Account Managers, Sales, Legal, Marketing, User Ops and others to address product needs and user queries&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Be responsible for reviewing and providing guidance on internal processes or external user communications drafted by marketing and/or user operations teams to ensure clear and helpful documentation related to any tax issue/process is made available for both internal and external use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Assist with gathering product feedback directly from users&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Monitor developments of 1099 policies, including similar reporting regimes worldwide&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Analyze current and proposed tax policy changes, evaluate tax product impacts, and develop and execute plans accordingly&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Support the ongoing maintenance and enhancements of the 1099 tax product&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Research tax technical and operational topics, and correspond with taxing authorities where necessary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;8-10+ years of 1099-K, 1099-MISC, and 1099-NEC experience, with a very strong preference for individuals with a combination of both in-house experience and accounting/law firm&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A very strong understanding of the U.S. rules around information reporting and withholding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Deep experience with all elements of an end-to-end the 1099 reporting process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills.&amp;nbsp; You should be able to adjust your communication style based on your audience (users, product teams, engineers, advisors, etc.).&amp;nbsp; In this role you will be required to translate tax laws into tax requirements for product and engineer teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The ability to prioritize projects in a fast-changing environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A desire to tackle complex problems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Empathy, humility and some comedy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;An advanced degree or professional qualification (CPA, JD or equivalent, Masters in Tax, or LLM or equivalent) in tax or law&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Knowledge of leading 1099 compliance practices and technology solutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Project-related experience building 1099 reporting processes with engineering teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working in a high-growth, rapidly scaling environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working in technology, payments, or financial services&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A willingness to work with a diverse crew of tax nerds who care deeply about Stripe’s tax issues and each other&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please include these with your application:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A resume and LinkedIn profile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;',
