    title: 'Account Associate',
    content:
      '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Account Associate team is a highly consultative group that manages relationships with and is responsible for the growth and retention of Stripe’s largest and fastest growing Startup and SMB customers. As an Account Associate, you’ll identify opportunities for our clients to get the most out of Stripe by quickly understanding our clients’ needs, managing upsell and renewal opportunities, and driving end-to-end campaigns to increase adoption of Stripe’s offering. We’re looking for a well-rounded strategic operator who can build strong relationships with Stripe’s clients and manage projects to engage with customers at scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;If you’re hungry, smart, persistent, and a great teammate, we want to hear from you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ll:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop and implement strategies for driving product adoption and client retention at scale among existing Stripe customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Solve complex client needs and work across product, sales, risk, and operations teams to improve our product&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Manage contract renewals and lead commercial negotiations with our clients&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Retain and increase revenue and market share with existing accounts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for someone who has:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;3+ years of experience in a client-facing role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to understand complex technical ecosystems and build great relationships with technical customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to drive upsell opportunities for additional Stripe products in long-term, consultative engagements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Analytical ability to manage complex pricing and cost considerations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience managing projects with input from cross-functional teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A knack for working well with a wide range of people, both internally and externally&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability and motivation to operate in a highly ambiguous and fast-paced environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Superior verbal and written communication skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Prior experience in a customer-facing role at a high growth technology company&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with Excel and SQL, or a willingness to learn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;',
